headline: Jennifer Silberman joins Operation Homefront's National Board of Directors
summary: Operation Homefront, a leading national military nonprofit dedicated to serving America's military families, has elected Dollar Tree Senior Vice President, Chief Sustainability and Corporate Affairs Officer Jennifer Silberman to its national board of directors. Silberman, with 30 years of global experience, leads Dollar Tree's culture and belonging, public affairs, social impact, and sustainability efforts – ensuring the initiatives she leads connect to Dollar Tree's business priorities and long
